            "creation_date": 1499907684,
            "body": "<p>Make sure you have the Numbers activity exists and is in your Android.manifest.<\/p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>All activities must be represented by  elements in the manifest file. Any that are not declared there will not be seen by the system and will never be run.<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n",
            "answer_id": 45069806,
            "question_id": 45069631
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://i.sstatic.net/gT2r0.png?s=256",
                "account_id": 3695702,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 5156075,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/5156075/john-joe",
