            "score": 0,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1499908626,
            "creation_date": 1499908626,
            "body": "<p>First, you are not initialized your <code>TextView<\/code><\/p>\n\n<pre><code>textView = (TextView)findViewById(R.id.numbers)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Second, as others suggested, add <strong>Numbers<\/strong> activity in your <code>Android.manifest<\/code><\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 45069917,
            "question_id": 45069631
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/a6ab91233e2e644ba5ea1265f36555d5?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
