            "last_activity_date": 1499908735,
            "creation_date": 1499908735,
            "body": "<p>You did not add the  clickable attribute, without it, the click handler isn't called. So, add it...<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>...\n\n&lt;TextView\n        android:id=\"@+id/numbers\"\n        style=\"@style/CategoryStyle\"\n        android:layout_marginBottom=\"16dp\"\n        android:background=\"@drawable/numbers\"\n        android:text=\"@string/category_numbers\"\n        android:onClick=\"openNumbersList\"\n        android:clickable=\"true\"/&gt;\n\n...\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 45069934,
            "question_id": 45069631
        },
